Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14086] allowed 
``group-by``
 and 
``split-by``
 to work with other values
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14082] added rendered and json error messages in try/catch
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14077] reverted "Add the 
``history import``
 command"
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14072] added 
``like``
 and 
``not-like``
 operators as synonyms for the regex operators 
``=~``
 and 
``!~``
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14120] fixed an issue with the last exit code not being set
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14081] fixed keybinding parsing
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14108] added count to uniq search terms
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14075] rate-limited save command progress bar updates
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14106] updated to rust 1.80.1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14104] implemented 
``polars unnest``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14093] bumped reedline to version 0.36
YizhePKU 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14105] reduced duplicate dependencies on the 
``windows``
 crate
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14085] made 
``plugin list``
 read state from plugin registry file as well
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14084] added a workflow to set milestone for a merged PR automatically
sgvictorino 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14074] ran ensure_flag_arg_type for short flag values
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14051] prevented 
``use``
 command from creating a variable with empty record if it doesn't define any constants
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13873] changed display_error.exit_code to false by default
